==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Etymology===
From French ''[[#French|agouti]]'' or Spanish ''[[aguti]]'', from Tupi-Guarani ''[[akutí]]''.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/əˈgu:ti/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#A [[rodent]] similar in appearance to a [[guinea pig]] but having longer [[leg]]s.

